♪ After all the jacks
are in their boxes♪

46:19.864 --> 46:22.257
♪ And the clowns have all♪

46:22.301 --> 46:25.347
♪ Gone to bed♪

46:25.391 --> 46:28.786
♪ You can hear happiness
staggering♪

46:28.829 --> 46:31.614
♪ On down the street♪

46:31.658 --> 46:33.834
♪ Footprints♪

46:33.878 --> 46:36.794
♪ Dressed in red♪

46:36.837 --> 46:38.970
♪ And the wind♪

46:39.013 --> 46:42.277
♪ Whispers, "Mary"♪

46:47.065 --> 46:50.198
♪ A broom is drearily♪

46:50.242 --> 46:52.722
♪ Sweeping♪

46:52.766 --> 46:54.594
♪ Up the broken pieces♪

46:54.637 --> 46:56.639
♪ Of yesterday's life♪

